{"id": 2131, "genre": 1001, "title": "从小到大，你的死亡教育都是从哪里获得的？", "description": "死亡长什么样子，在真正见识过死亡之前我们其实知道并不多。（Giphy）", "record_count": 1569, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180119104101DulIEXAeCtp8S1mn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 262656, "content": "记得是小时候看  遗失的美好  MV突然想到自己会长大，爸妈会生老病死，在我之前过世，只留下孤零零的我一个人，瞬间眼泪哗哗的往外流。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 260864, "content": "宠物离世，上一秒还是温热的，下一秒就僵硬了，人也是一样的吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130512}, {"id": 260865, "content": "基友分手。生离胜死别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 260866, "content": "看电影里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244055}, {"id": 262147, "content": "看书《那天蓝色的彼岸》", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247533}, {"id": 260867, "content": "我觉得死亡可能是人从一种形态进去另外一种形态，精神不灭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244060}, {"id": 260868, "content": "大学朋友，毕业后我回国了，他还留在泰国，有次和他聊天，他告诉我他脑力长了恶性肿瘤，压迫神经，和他视频的时候他已经有一只眼皮无法睁开了，他后来回国治疗，那段时间工作特比忙，没怎么联系，最后是在他的qq空间上看见她妹妹的留言，说他已经在12月12日去世了，偶尔会给他发微信，说说话，虽然已经不会再有回复了", "image": "img/option/option/20180122162731c7LQFKqxubjeyaU8.jpg", "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2941}, {"id": 261124, "content": "书 电影 电视 有些是很荒谬的 那种事没啥营养的东西  但是有些作品的影响非常大 那是真的经过有深度的人思考的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194970}, {"id": 261125, "content": "“雪孩子是个恐怖故事。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235638}, {"id": 260870, "content": "看暮光之城时感悟的吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244071}, {"id": 260871, "content": "倩女幽魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618373}, {"id": 260873, "content": "大概是，侥幸没死之后一段时间的脑洞时间吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204679}, {"id": 260874, "content": "真正意义上的死亡教育，是读大学的时候通过自己阅读得到的，其实在中国教育中，大部分人是没有得到过死亡教育的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215719}, {"id": 260875, "content": "同学胃癌离世，知道的时候已是晚期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244065}, {"id": 260876, "content": "心理学课", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689408}, {"id": 260877, "content": "电影吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749967}, {"id": 262671, "content": "去国外实习短短三个月，回国后，我没有妈妈了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 260880, "content": "从记事开始，就很惧怕死亡，不知道为什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670837}, {"id": 260881, "content": "生死由命 富贵在天\n最亲的亲人离世 妄想有奇迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239801}, {"id": 261137, "content": "当我想活的更好点时就必须思考好有关死亡的问题，可惜能教导我关于死亡话题的人物却不多，因为能教导我的都没死，死去的又无法教导了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244997}, {"id": 260883, "content": "吃垃圾食品的时候被爸妈吓唬马上就要死了，吓哭回房间安顿我的“遗物”给玩偶们", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169549}, {"id": 260885, "content": "子欲养而亲不待", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242625}, {"id": 260886, "content": "两次差点挂了，一次溺水一次骑自行车骑快了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243843}, {"id": 260887, "content": "电影电视剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242911}, {"id": 261655, "content": "看多了车祸现场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911176}, {"id": 260888, "content": "濒死体验", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399953}, {"id": 260889, "content": "死亡是必然的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932903}, {"id": 260890, "content": "书 电影 电视", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334123}, {"id": 261146, "content": "换同桌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245025}, {"id": 260891, "content": "随着年龄增长，亲人不断离世；随着工业发展，道路越来越宽，车祸也越来越多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039344}, {"id": 260892, "content": "绿灯过马路前面的人被撞飞?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178787}, {"id": 260893, "content": "影视剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237440}, {"id": 260894, "content": "奶奶去世那天早上，我堂哥喊我说奶奶有点不好你来看看，我习以为常的感觉应该没什么大事就没去看，谁知半个小时后奶奶离世，回忆一瞬间冲洗着我的大脑，泪水如一瞬间打湿了我的脸颊，那几天哭的天昏地暗，自己未曾为奶奶付出任何回报。失去过后才懂得珍惜  为时已晚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244125}, {"id": 261406, "content": "小时候路过火灾现场，看到被大火烧死的死者，自那以后我不敢用火柴，对生命充满敬畏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245595}, {"id": 260895, "content": "《最好的告别:关于衰老与死亡》\n其实衰老才是长期真正难面对的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807000}, {"id": 261151, "content": "死亡，，或许是什么东西突然间发现它已不见了，，不管怎样呐喊，怎样狂奔，，到头来，都找不回来了，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245042}, {"id": 260896, "content": "小学生300字作文？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223885}, {"id": 260897, "content": "九岁的时候，我妈去世了，当时觉得也没什么，一滴泪都没掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185153}, {"id": 260898, "content": "初中班主任说过，“人啊，一出生就是奔着死去的。”", "image": "img/option/option/20180122181611mCL8iNxQR93GglAK", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1193184}, {"id": 260900, "content": "两个亲人同时车祸去世 开始审视生命和死亡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242424}, {"id": 262437, "content": "电影，还有和朋友们聊天讨论", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249497}, {"id": 261926, "content": "知道多来a梦的结局是大雄是神经病幻想了一切之后很多人跳楼了，恍然觉得人生也不过是幻象", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246727}, {"id": 262184, "content": "小时候有过几次休克，突然就没有意识，突然就醒了，小时候上吊（我就是自己闲着没事做，不是脑袋有问题）那种窒息的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103848}, {"id": 260904, "content": "父母参加的葬礼逐渐变多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203912}, {"id": 260905, "content": "电视剧算不算～", "image": "img/option/option/20180122183010oM2Owx6mVvYnZR3d.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237165}, {"id": 261162, "content": "车祸，火灾，水患\n天灾人祸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245093}, {"id": 260907, "content": "七龙珠？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103855}, {"id": 260908, "content": "高速堵车目击车祸现场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715726}, {"id": 260909, "content": "很小的时候弄死一只小虫子就知道，生命的渺小", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196654}, {"id": 261677, "content": "先是从句中 然后来自现实", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246053}]}